{"word":"H8401 - תֶּבֶן - teben - teh'-ben - Chaff","slug":"H8401","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">תֶּבֶן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>teben"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>teh'-ben"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Chaff"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05DF; - teben</b> - <i>teh'-ben</i><p/>Probably from <a href=\"#/H1129\">H1129</a>; properly <i>material</i>, that is, (specifically) refuse <i>haum</i> or stalks of grain (as <i>chopped</i> in threshing and used for fodder): - chaff, straw, stubble."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4963\">H4963</a>, <a href=\"#/H8402\">H8402</a>, <a href=\"#/H8405\">H8405</a>, <a href=\"#/H8407\">H8407</a>, <a href=\"#/H8412\">H8412</a>, <a href=\"#/H8413\">H8413</a>, <a href=\"#/H8425\">H8425</a>"}]}